{"tid":724390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本政府: 北韓在解決核武問題毫無進展","createTime":"2018-07-01T01:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T11:15:21.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c13796fcaf0657bc5a11ed9e64c00d0d805498f2","tid":724390,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T01:26:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1404506-20180630.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1404506-20180630.htm&d=lLMyZ9h7LKaY64DoX5tA3C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=df4469c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1404506-20180630.htm&h=ac5e5696\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1404506-20180630.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n 日防衛相指北韓至今未銷毀任何核武及彈道導彈<br />\n2018-06-30 HKT 22:50<br />\n<br />\n日本防衛相小野寺五典表示，北韓在解決核武及導彈問題毫無進展，至今仍未銷毀任何可抵達日本的彈道導彈，亦未移交過核彈頭，形容什麼都沒有進展。<br />\n<br />\n小野寺五典在山口縣演講，提到日本不應放鬆對北韓的警惕，又強調有必要引入「陸上神盾」導彈攔截系統。小野寺五典表示，部署防禦系統需要花相當長的時間，而北韓可能一瞬間改變態度不再對話，日本不到最後都不可以鬆懈。"},{"pid":"0f350e97008397efd3c2186f379bbf594338d808","tid":724390,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T01:51:44.000Z","msg":"金仔又係拖時間姐"},{"pid":"b6876363adfb6266c4e48dfb761aef04cc04afb2","tid":724390,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T01:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Trump又中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b2ac2b7d0d91bbc3f7adbc536f7391017aa701","tid":724390,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}